summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Lots 21 to 24 inclusive, Block 30, Boston Company's Plat, and Lots 22 to 24 inclusive, Block 58, Denny and Hoyt's Addition, with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-182 and 17-132, respectively.
